Description:
Over 40 years of expertise. TESI designs, manufactures and distributes products and accessories for Energy, Oil&Gas, Petrochemical and Chemical industries.
From our UAE branch, TESI Middle East, our three business divisions sell, lease and service:
-CORROSION PREVENTION COATINGS for protection of inshore and offshore Piling Splash Zone;
-PIPELINE EQUIPMENT for Heat Treatments, Welding, Blasting, FBE Coating, in-house or on-site Custom Coating for Spools;
-IGNITION SYSTEMS for Industrial Burners, Gas Flaring and other combustion processes.

